::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:middle
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:13.990 --> 00:00:19.250
One Piece

3
00:00:14.830 --> 00:00:19.250
Wano Arc

4
00:01:41.580 --> 00:01:44.210
<b>Seppuku</b>

5
00:02:54.360 --> 00:03:01.790
<b>Wano Country</b>

6
00:03:02.910 --> 00:03:05.920
Want some freshwater clams?!

7
00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:07.750
Outta the way!

8
00:03:11.630 --> 00:03:13.380
Come in! Come in!

9
00:03:13.380 --> 00:03:15.510
Try our special flower udon!

10
00:03:50.590 --> 00:03:54.840
We're short-handed here.
Could you help me a little bit?

11
00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:57.340
Hey! Carry the other end!

12
00:03:57.970 --> 00:04:00.220
Hey, hey, hey!

13
00:04:00.220 --> 00:04:02.510
New guy!

14
00:04:02.510 --> 00:04:06.230
You're the one who did this part?!

15
00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:09.310
Yes, Boss!

16
00:04:09.730 --> 00:04:11.270
Is there something wrong?

17
00:04:11.730 --> 00:04:15.490
What kind of idiot are you?!

18
00:04:15.490 --> 00:04:17.570
It's perfection!

19
00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:19.700
I'm praising you!

20
00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:23.700
You damn fool!

21
00:04:23.700 --> 00:04:26.410
Of course, it's perfect because I...!

22
00:04:26.790 --> 00:04:28.290
...play your roles!

23
00:04:32.380 --> 00:04:34.380
O-O-Oh...

24
00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:36.760
I'm pleased to hear it!

25
00:04:36.760 --> 00:04:38.840
Thank you, sir!

26
00:04:39.970 --> 00:04:42.720
You damn blowhard!

27
00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:45.800
<b>Franosuke



Carpenter</b>

28
00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:48.770
Everyone!

29
00:04:48.770 --> 00:04:51.730
Gather 'round! Gather 'round!

30
00:04:51.730 --> 00:04:55.690
Here's a sheet of paper—
no gimmicks or setup!

31
00:04:55.690 --> 00:04:58.070
One sheet becomes two!

32
00:04:58.070 --> 00:05:01.860
Two sheets become four!
Four sheets become eight!

33
00:05:01.860 --> 00:05:07.250
Eight to sixteen, then thirty-two to sixty-four!

34
00:05:09.790 --> 00:05:12.380
I give you the fluttering dance of...

35
00:05:12.380 --> 00:05:19.630
a springtime sakura shower
and the snowfall of Wano's early evening!

36
00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:33.560
Now you've witnessed how
truly sharp this named blade is!

37
00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:35.690
A simple graze from it...

38
00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:39.030
See how easily it can cut you!

39
00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:48.370
But, watch this!

40
00:05:49.250 --> 00:05:52.210
What I have here is toad oil!

41
00:05:52.670 --> 00:05:56.340
If you apply it to a wound...!

42
00:05:59.130 --> 00:06:01.170
Ta-dah!

43
00:06:01.510 --> 00:06:04.090
Look! You see?!

44
00:06:04.090 --> 00:06:06.720
This is how it works!

45
00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:08.760
The bleeding's stopped, too!

46
00:06:09.390 --> 00:06:11.850
This toad oil is an East Blue specialty!

47
00:06:11.850 --> 00:06:13.940
Come and get some!

48
00:06:13.940 --> 00:06:15.730
– I'll have some!
– Me too!

49
00:06:15.730 --> 00:06:18.190
You folks have a good eye!

50
00:06:18.190 --> 00:06:22.070
Now, gather 'round! Gather 'round!

51
00:06:22.030 --> 00:06:25.450
<b>Usohachi



Toad Oil

Salesman</b>

52
00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:34.370
You're doing great!

53
00:06:34.370 --> 00:06:38.630
That's it! That's it! So irresistible!

54
00:06:42.130 --> 00:06:43.630
Your hand is too low!

55
00:06:43.970 --> 00:06:46.550
Lower your hips more!

56
00:06:48.470 --> 00:06:49.850
Yes, ma'am...

57
00:06:49.850 --> 00:06:55.390
Your goal is nearly impossible,
so you have to push yourself!

58
00:06:55.390 --> 00:07:01.110
At this rate, the shogun won't invite
you to his court in the time desired!

59
00:07:07.780 --> 00:07:10.330
Keep going, baby!

60
00:07:13.960 --> 00:07:15.120
Yes, ma'am...

61
00:07:15.790 --> 00:07:19.920
<b>Orobi



Geisha</b>

62
00:07:31.010 --> 00:07:33.140
This sake is delicious.

63
00:07:35.140 --> 00:07:39.180
<b>Zorojuro



Ronin</b>

64
00:07:39.730 --> 00:07:40.940
I'll come back soon!

65
00:07:40.940 --> 00:07:42.440
Thank you very much!

66
00:07:50.370 --> 00:07:52.830
The moon's beautiful...

67
00:08:12.930 --> 00:08:15.270
No!

68
00:08:22.400 --> 00:08:23.320
Move!

69
00:08:25.400 --> 00:08:27.320
The smell of blood...

70
00:08:27.990 --> 00:08:28.900
Hold it!

71
00:08:30.910 --> 00:08:32.990
That's a nice smell, buddy.

72
00:08:33.620 --> 00:08:37.540
Like a blood-scented perfume...

73
00:08:47.880 --> 00:08:50.800
– You're under arrest!
– You're under arrest!
"Arrest"

74
00:08:50.800 --> 00:08:54.510
Yeah, the slasher went that way.

75
00:08:54.510 --> 00:08:57.140
You're under arrest! You're under arrest!

76
00:08:57.140 --> 00:08:57.770
Huh?

77
00:08:57.770 --> 00:09:00.310
You're the slasher! Don't resist!

78
00:09:00.310 --> 00:09:01.480
Huh?!

79
00:09:01.480 --> 00:09:07.150
– You're under arrest! You're under arrest!
– You're under arrest! You're under arrest!

80
00:09:10.030 --> 00:09:12.530
Looks like I'll have to stamp out these sparks...

81
00:09:12.990 --> 00:09:16.290
before they flare up!

82
00:09:16.290 --> 00:09:17.870
...play your roles!

83
00:09:20.040 --> 00:09:22.210
Listen, everyone.

84
00:09:22.210 --> 00:09:23.580
You're in Wano now.

85
00:09:24.130 --> 00:09:26.130
The shogun of this land is...

86
00:09:26.130 --> 00:09:28.760
Kurozumi Orochi!

87
00:09:30.090 --> 00:09:36.390
All of his officials are under
the control of Kaido.

88
00:09:36.390 --> 00:09:40.310
That's what makes them all so high-handed.

89
00:09:41.060 --> 00:09:45.820
Therefore, if you even touch them,
Kaido will hear about it!

90
00:09:46.190 --> 00:09:50.610
Until all of our allies get here
and we're ready to fight,

91
00:09:51.110 --> 00:09:54.450
we cannot afford to be discovered!

92
00:09:54.950 --> 00:09:58.160
So you must all pretend
to be regular citizens for now...

93
00:09:58.540 --> 00:10:01.710
and quietly—I repeat, quietly—

94
00:10:01.710 --> 00:10:05.750
play your roles!

95
00:10:08.920 --> 00:10:10.710
I guess I have no choice...

96
00:10:10.710 --> 00:10:12.090
I got it...

97
00:10:12.090 --> 00:10:13.760
verily...

98
00:10:13.760 --> 00:10:15.180
Hey, tie him up!

99
00:10:15.180 --> 00:10:18.930
– You're under arrest! You're under arrest!
– You're under arrest! You're under arrest!

100
00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:29.780
It's the arch rogue who's been
terrorizing our streets!

101
00:10:29.780 --> 00:10:33.860
The magistrate has finally,
finally captured him!

102
00:10:33.860 --> 00:10:36.740
The criminal has been sentenced to seppuku!

103
00:10:36.740 --> 00:10:39.410
You can get all the details in here!

104
00:10:39.410 --> 00:10:41.450
I hate his guts!

105
00:10:41.450 --> 00:10:44.290
He turned his blade against my husband too!

106
00:10:44.290 --> 00:10:46.130
What a relief!

107
00:10:46.130 --> 00:10:50.250
Just this month, he slashed
three people on the streets at night.

108
00:10:53.880 --> 00:10:56.970
Hey, can I have one, too?!

109
00:10:56.970 --> 00:10:58.180
Thank you!

110
00:10:59.350 --> 00:11:02.520
Z-Zorojuro...
"The Slasher, Zorojuro"

111
00:11:10.610 --> 00:11:14.030
So your name is Zorojuro...

112
00:11:15.110 --> 00:11:19.490
Everyone was fearful of the slasher...

113
00:11:19.490 --> 00:11:24.120
If you slash your belly,
the town will become peaceful again.

114
00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:29.250
And I can hardly believe...

115
00:11:29.790 --> 00:11:33.010
you're also a grave robber.

116
00:11:33.670 --> 00:11:35.880
Twenty-three years ago...

117
00:11:36.430 --> 00:11:39.800
amid the confusion of a pirate incident...

118
00:11:39.800 --> 00:11:43.520
the corpse of the legendary swordsman Ryuma went missing...

119
00:11:44.180 --> 00:11:46.440
along with his named blade Shusui!

120
00:11:47.730 --> 00:11:52.690
Legend has it that Ryuma sliced off
the head of a giant, savage dragon...

121
00:11:53.190 --> 00:11:56.700
with this very sword, Shusui.

122
00:11:58.990 --> 00:12:02.370
Although, slasher...

123
00:12:02.990 --> 00:12:06.580
That grave robbery took place
twenty-three years ago.

124
00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:09.540
You don't look that old.

125
00:12:10.040 --> 00:12:12.290
Did you steal it from the original thief?

126
00:12:15.340 --> 00:12:16.970
Oh, well...

127
00:12:16.970 --> 00:12:21.390
The famous Shusui is now in my hands!

128
00:12:26.680 --> 00:12:27.940
Yes, sir.

129
00:12:27.940 --> 00:12:31.310
Now, Zorojuro, it's time.

130
00:12:35.690 --> 00:12:36.740
Hey.

131
00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:39.530
This blade has no grip...

132
00:12:42.870 --> 00:12:44.160
verily.

133
00:12:44.160 --> 00:12:48.540
A seppuku blade is usually short
and has no grip.

134
00:12:48.540 --> 00:12:52.170
It's not meant for combat after all.

135
00:12:52.170 --> 00:12:56.590
Do you know the proper etiquette of seppuku?

136
00:12:57.170 --> 00:13:02.510
If you call yourself a samurai,
admit your guilt and kill yourself honorably!

137
00:13:02.850 --> 00:13:05.600
Before you start suffering...

138
00:13:06.720 --> 00:13:09.020
I'll assist in your death!

139
00:13:28.620 --> 00:13:30.330
Well then...

140
00:13:30.330 --> 00:13:31.460
So long.

141
00:13:34.540 --> 00:13:36.840
Just don't cry like a baby...

142
00:13:37.460 --> 00:13:42.050
A proper death is a samurai's honor.

143
00:13:42.590 --> 00:13:44.640
We have witnesses!

144
00:13:44.640 --> 00:13:46.390
And enough evidence!

145
00:13:46.970 --> 00:13:50.600
This will be an honorable death
that you don't deserve!

146
00:13:51.560 --> 00:13:54.520
Be happy that you can perform seppuku.

147
00:14:10.790 --> 00:14:13.330
I smell blood.

148
00:14:16.920 --> 00:14:18.300
You...

149
00:14:19.880 --> 00:14:21.380
are the culprit!

150
00:14:49.120 --> 00:14:52.580
I'm sorry, Kin'emon.

151
00:15:13.100 --> 00:15:15.520
Ouch!

152
00:15:31.370 --> 00:15:34.330
Is this... Wano?

153
00:15:51.310 --> 00:15:53.640
Where did everyone go?

154
00:15:54.680 --> 00:15:56.600
Let's see...

155
00:15:57.350 --> 00:16:00.560
What happened to us?

156
00:16:08.030 --> 00:16:10.320
Get him! Get him!

157
00:17:16.890 --> 00:17:18.100
What the?!

158
00:17:30.650 --> 00:17:31.410
Hey!

159
00:17:35.240 --> 00:17:36.290
Hey, you!

160
00:17:36.290 --> 00:17:38.790
Don't break our ship!

161
00:17:40.410 --> 00:17:42.000
It's a giant dog!

162
00:17:45.040 --> 00:17:47.710
Is it a dog or a boar?

163
00:18:05.020 --> 00:18:07.980
<b>A Baboon</b>

164
00:18:13.740 --> 00:18:15.990
An animal with a sword?

165
00:18:15.990 --> 00:18:18.740
I guess that's just how Wano is!

166
00:18:25.750 --> 00:18:30.460
The first thing I see here is
a fight between two wild beasts?

167
00:18:58.410 --> 00:19:00.160
Listen, guys!

168
00:19:00.160 --> 00:19:03.460
You can fight all you want
but don't damage the ship!

169
00:19:09.130 --> 00:19:10.460
Oh, yeah...

170
00:19:13.090 --> 00:19:15.550
What was I doing?

171
00:19:21.010 --> 00:19:25.060
After we climbed up
the waterfall, we saw land...

172
00:19:25.060 --> 00:19:28.900
But we were sucked into a whirlpool
before getting there...

173
00:19:28.900 --> 00:19:30.610
What's this?!

174
00:19:30.610 --> 00:19:33.240
Hey, the tide is running in reverse!

175
00:19:34.700 --> 00:19:36.280
Hang in there, Sunny!

176
00:19:38.910 --> 00:19:41.160
Nami, hold onto me!

177
00:19:41.160 --> 00:19:42.990
Thank you, Sanji!

178
00:19:42.990 --> 00:19:45.620
You're most welcome, Nami!

179
00:19:45.620 --> 00:19:46.920
Sanji!

180
00:19:46.920 --> 00:19:48.330
Yeah, hold onto me!

181
00:19:48.330 --> 00:19:51.000
Okay, I'm gonna jump to land!

182
00:19:52.800 --> 00:19:53.800
Ready?!

183
00:19:53.800 --> 00:19:55.590
Wait, Sanji!

184
00:19:57.590 --> 00:20:00.430
Take me with you!

185
00:20:00.430 --> 00:20:01.930
Chobro!

186
00:20:01.930 --> 00:20:03.430
I can't! Too heavy!

187
00:20:03.430 --> 00:20:06.850
No! Don't leave me behind!

188
00:20:07.310 --> 00:20:09.310
I'm sorry, but you need to let go.

189
00:20:10.560 --> 00:20:13.070
How could you...?!

190
00:20:13.530 --> 00:20:14.860
Just kidding.

191
00:20:14.860 --> 00:20:16.400
Hold on tightly!

192
00:20:16.400 --> 00:20:17.820
Sanji!

193
00:20:20.120 --> 00:20:22.830
Then allow me to join, too.

194
00:20:23.950 --> 00:20:25.580
I love you all!

195
00:20:25.580 --> 00:20:27.460
Squeeze!

196
00:20:27.790 --> 00:20:30.040
Those are some hard bones!

197
00:20:30.040 --> 00:20:32.880
Not bones! Bones are so creepy!

198
00:20:33.300 --> 00:20:35.380
Use my belly, Sanji!

199
00:20:37.760 --> 00:20:39.090
Okay!

200
00:20:43.510 --> 00:20:44.720
See you later!

201
00:20:44.720 --> 00:20:47.310
Yeah, I'm right behind you!

202
00:20:50.690 --> 00:20:52.940
Alright, it's my turn to go!

203
00:20:52.940 --> 00:20:55.980
Sunny! I promise I'll find you later!

204
00:21:01.950 --> 00:21:04.410
Here I go!

205
00:21:07.250 --> 00:21:09.120
The octopus?!

206
00:21:09.710 --> 00:21:13.790
What do you still want from me?!

207
00:21:13.790 --> 00:21:17.800
Damn octopus!

208
00:21:30.980 --> 00:21:34.060
Then, I was here when I woke up.

209
00:21:34.770 --> 00:21:37.780
So am I above the waterfall? Or did I fall?

210
00:21:37.780 --> 00:21:40.700
Did I make it to Wano?

211
00:21:47.950 --> 00:21:48.830
Oh?

212
00:21:48.830 --> 00:21:50.370
The vivre card is gone!

213
00:21:51.830 --> 00:21:53.500
I lost it!

214
00:21:53.500 --> 00:21:55.090
Is it in the sea?!

215
00:21:55.670 --> 00:21:57.960
Damn!

216
00:22:01.340 --> 00:22:02.590
Oh, well!

217
00:22:02.590 --> 00:22:03.550
Forget it.

218
00:22:03.550 --> 00:22:05.640
Stop!

219
00:22:05.640 --> 00:22:10.390
Let me go! I didn't say anything like that!

220
00:22:10.390 --> 00:22:12.940
Give me back my rice, too!

221
00:22:13.350 --> 00:22:15.560
No, I'm sure you said it!

222
00:22:16.230 --> 00:22:21.320
When the Kozuki Clan comes back,
they'll teach you a lesson!

223
00:22:21.320 --> 00:22:22.950
You traitor...

224
00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:28.160
You're an ally of that evil
family, the Kozuki Clan!

225
00:22:28.160 --> 00:22:30.000
It's a serious crime!

226
00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:32.870
We'll either sell you to a brothel
or send you to prison.

227
00:22:32.870 --> 00:22:33.960
There'll be no mercy!

228
00:22:34.540 --> 00:22:35.710
But...!

229
00:22:35.710 --> 00:22:37.460
Pipe down for a second.

230
00:22:37.880 --> 00:22:39.840
We're on duty now!

231
00:22:42.630 --> 00:22:44.470
Look! There's a ship on the beach!

232
00:22:44.470 --> 00:22:46.550
Just one survivor?

233
00:22:46.550 --> 00:22:49.640
And our baboon's having
trouble with that lion-dog!

234
00:22:49.640 --> 00:22:52.060
He's not so dependable as a guard, huh?

235
00:22:53.560 --> 00:22:55.230
Oh! Komachiyo?!

236
00:22:58.820 --> 00:23:01.190
Guys, that's enough...

237
00:23:01.190 --> 00:23:03.860
Boss! Looks like the report was right!

238
00:23:03.860 --> 00:23:05.490
It's the trespassing ship!

239
00:23:05.910 --> 00:23:07.320
Do you see its crew?

240
00:23:07.320 --> 00:23:08.620
There's just one.

241
00:23:08.990 --> 00:23:10.370
One, huh?

242
00:23:10.370 --> 00:23:13.120
We'll knock him out and take him with us!

243
00:23:13.120 --> 00:23:15.710
He'll at least become our laborer!

244
00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:23.380
Good boy. Sleep well!

245
00:23:24.760 --> 00:23:29.300
When you wake up, we'll treat
you so well as our slave!

246
00:23:44.610 --> 00:23:45.530
What the...?!

247
00:23:50.910 --> 00:23:52.700
Attacking me all of a sudden?

248
00:23:52.700 --> 00:23:54.250
You bastard!

249
00:23:59.080 --> 00:24:00.790
I can't hit him!

250
00:24:01.800 --> 00:24:03.800
Hey, what's going on?

251
00:24:03.800 --> 00:24:05.630
Well, it's nothing...

252
00:24:22.150 --> 00:24:24.860
This beach is so rowdy.

253
00:24:25.320 --> 00:24:26.740
Dammit...

254
00:24:27.360 --> 00:24:28.990
Hey, baboon!

255
00:24:28.990 --> 00:24:31.910
Don't just stand there and watch!

256
00:24:32.280 --> 00:24:33.990
You can get the lion-dog later!

257
00:24:33.990 --> 00:24:35.580
Catch that guy!

258
00:24:40.580 --> 00:24:42.920
Actually, you now have permission...

259
00:24:42.920 --> 00:24:44.420
to kill him!

260
00:25:15.990 --> 00:25:17.410
What do you want?

261
00:25:47.280 --> 00:25:48.230
Good!

262
00:25:48.230 --> 00:25:51.360
Don't fight so much, guys!

263
00:25:54.450 --> 00:25:57.200
What the hell are you afraid of?!

264
00:25:57.200 --> 00:25:59.790
He's just a lousy pirate!

265
00:26:13.510 --> 00:26:17.680
Look what you did, you squirt!

266
00:26:18.260 --> 00:26:20.310
I'll kill you!

267
00:26:21.390 --> 00:26:23.770
Stop right there, you damn brat!

268
00:26:23.770 --> 00:26:25.610
F-Forgive me!

269
00:26:32.900 --> 00:26:36.240
I surrender!

270
00:26:37.530 --> 00:26:39.740
What are you doing?

271
00:26:39.740 --> 00:26:42.120
I said I surrender!

272
00:26:42.120 --> 00:26:44.500
I surrender!

273
00:26:44.750 --> 00:26:48.090
<b>Otama</b>

274
00:26:49.090 --> 00:26:51.420
I'm not gonna do anything to you!

275
00:26:51.420 --> 00:26:54.380
Y-You mean it?

276
00:26:54.800 --> 00:26:56.260
Yeah!

277
00:26:56.260 --> 00:26:58.220
U-Um...

278
00:26:58.720 --> 00:27:03.560
I'm sorry but while you're here,
may I have some of your time?

279
00:27:03.560 --> 00:27:05.230
Th-This is my chance!

280
00:27:06.190 --> 00:27:08.730
Chance? What do you mean?

281
00:27:08.730 --> 00:27:10.440
All right. Let's do it.

282
00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:11.900
Huh? Do what?

283
00:27:12.240 --> 00:27:15.160
Millet Dumpling!

284
00:27:18.410 --> 00:27:20.160
Here we go!

285
00:27:20.160 --> 00:27:21.080
What?!

286
00:27:21.080 --> 00:27:23.080
Your cheek came off!

287
00:27:27.630 --> 00:27:29.340
Go ahead. Eat it.

288
00:27:39.050 --> 00:27:41.010
Wh-What are you doing?

289
00:27:55.530 --> 00:27:56.740
Shake.

290
00:28:01.490 --> 00:28:02.490
What?!

291
00:28:02.490 --> 00:28:05.210
She tamed that beast!

292
00:28:05.210 --> 00:28:06.960
I did it!

293
00:28:07.330 --> 00:28:12.920
I finally befriended
the savage mountain baboon!

294
00:28:12.920 --> 00:28:13.960
Yay!

295
00:28:13.960 --> 00:28:16.090
I did it!

296
00:28:16.090 --> 00:28:18.220
So you're an ability user!

297
00:28:18.220 --> 00:28:20.550
That power's pretty handy!

298
00:28:25.520 --> 00:28:26.680
Okay, okay.

299
00:28:26.680 --> 00:28:29.020
You're our friend now!

300
00:28:31.440 --> 00:28:32.770
Good boy.

301
00:28:32.770 --> 00:28:34.650
Is that your dog?

302
00:28:35.400 --> 00:28:36.820
He is!

303
00:28:36.820 --> 00:28:38.860
I named him Komachiyo!

304
00:28:40.280 --> 00:28:42.410
Oh, Komachiyo!

305
00:28:42.410 --> 00:28:43.530
Nice to meet you!

306
00:28:43.530 --> 00:28:45.540
I'm Luffy!

307
00:28:49.580 --> 00:28:52.090
And my name is Otama.

308
00:28:52.920 --> 00:28:54.840
Okay, Otama!

309
00:28:54.840 --> 00:28:56.260
Nice to meet you, too!

310
00:28:56.260 --> 00:28:58.050
Nice to meet you!

311
00:28:58.050 --> 00:28:58.720
Now...

312
00:28:58.720 --> 00:29:02.930
I need to know if this country is Wano or not.

313
00:29:03.390 --> 00:29:05.060
This country?

314
00:29:06.470 --> 00:29:09.810
Yes, this is Wano!

315
00:29:10.140 --> 00:29:14.020
You're in the Kuri region of Wano...

316
00:29:14.020 --> 00:29:15.400
Big Bro!

317
00:29:15.400 --> 00:29:18.530
So I am in Wano!

318
00:29:19.320 --> 00:29:22.910
I finally made it to Wano!

319
00:29:23.240 --> 00:29:25.620
Wait for me, Kaido!

320
00:29:25.620 --> 00:29:27.290
Wait! "Big Bro"?!

321
00:29:27.700 --> 00:29:28.410
Hey!

322
00:29:28.410 --> 00:29:30.620
Since when am I your big brother?!

323
00:29:31.960 --> 00:29:34.090
A big brother is a big brother!

324
00:29:34.420 --> 00:29:35.920
What does that even mean?

325
00:29:35.920 --> 00:29:37.670
Well, it's no big deal.

326
00:29:37.670 --> 00:29:40.260
Okay, Big Bro!

327
00:29:53.980 --> 00:29:57.440
You committed a high crime, Zorojuro!

328
00:30:07.990 --> 00:30:09.700
Damn you, slasher!

329
00:30:09.700 --> 00:30:11.790
You won't even admit your guilt?!

330
00:30:31.810 --> 00:30:33.640
Three swords?!

331
00:30:33.640 --> 00:30:34.310
What?!

332
00:30:42.570 --> 00:30:44.110
Wh-What the...?!

333
00:30:44.110 --> 00:30:46.450
Dragon Twister!

334
00:31:23.320 --> 00:31:26.820
At least this country has some nice weather.

335
00:31:27.700 --> 00:31:31.450
Communication from Kuri beach
seems to have been cut.

336
00:31:31.450 --> 00:31:34.620
They were probably beaten by someone.

337
00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:36.830
We don't know how many there are.

338
00:31:38.000 --> 00:31:40.130
What should we do, Boss?

339
00:31:49.510 --> 00:31:52.010
Don't tell Kaido.

340
00:31:55.020 --> 00:31:56.850
I'll handle it!
